tile.space_warp_pad.description: The Warp Pad allows you to travel in the space dimension, when placed in a 3x3 configuration.
tile.rocket_crusher.description: Rocket Crusher will turn rockets into the advanced Heavy-Duty Plates. It is required to use in the rocket crafting bench.
tile.cheese_milk_cake.description: Cheese Milk Cakes are created from Cheese Milk Curds from Chalos, placeable and edible.
tile.dark_energy_receiver.description: Dark Energy Receivers will collect dark energy from a unknown distant planet in the galaxy, and can be used to create machine that handle dark energy. Dangerous!
tile.dark_energy_core.description: A powerful block from an unknown distant planet. Used for transform items into impossible things in the universe, by tossing item on top of the block.
tile.nuclear_waste_generator.description: The Nuclear Waste Generator will collect nuclear waste radiation in the area to produce power.
dark_energy_storage_cluster.description: Dark Energy Storage Cluster is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. Stores and outputs more energy than its predecessors.
nuclear_waste_energy_storage_cluster.des: Nuclear Waste Energy Storage Cluster is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. Stores and outputs more energy than its predecessors.
tile.dark_energy_generator.description: Dark Energy Generator will collect dark energy from an unknown distant planet or produce energy from a Dark Energy Pearl, storing it for further use.
tile.black_hole_storage.description: Black Hole Storage is a large item storage that uses gravity from a Black Hole to pull Item/EXP into itself. Items and EXP will not drop when break the block.
tile.shield_generator.description: Shield Generator will protect players from dangerous things (monsters, projectiles).
tile.sealable_nuclear_waste_rod.descript: Sealable blocks should be used where air cannot pass, such as space base walls.
item.infected_arrow.description: Can be obtained by throwing a normal arrow into infected water.
